# Style Guide

UI/UX design system and style guide for the Hindu Hate Index platform.

Should include:
- Color palette (neutral base, accent colors)
- Typography scale (headings, body text, data labels)
- Spacing system (8px grid)
- Component library (cards, buttons, forms, navigation)
- Icon set
- Responsive breakpoints
- Accessibility guidelines (WCAG 2.1 Level AA)
- Data visualization color schemes (colorblind-accessible)
